amalai\n|M-28\n|[[Government Tiruvannamalai Medical College and Hospital|Government Tiruvannamalai Medical College]]\n|co-worker of P30\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;background: #D3D3D3;\"|70-72\n!3\n| style=\"text-align:center;background:#ffff96;\"|'''T/PTP'''\n|\n|Villupuram\n|M\n|Government Villupuram Medical College Hospital\n| rowspan=\"3\" |attended Delhi religious  conference\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;background: #D3D3D3;\"|73-74\n!2\n| style=\"text-align:center;background:#ffff96;\"|'''T/PTP'''\n|\n|Madurai\n|M\n|Madurai MCH\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;background: #D3D3D3;\"|75-78\n!4\n| style=\"text-align:center;background:#ffff96;\"|'''T/PTP'''\n|\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Kanyakumari\n|M\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Government Kanyakumari Medical College Hospital\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;background: #D3D3D3;\"|79\n!1\n| style=\"text-align:center;background:#f5deb3;\" |'''PTP'''\n|\n|M-35\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;background: #D3D3D3;\"|80-101\n!22\n| style=\"text-align:center;background:#ffff96;\"|'''T/PTP'''\n|\n|Tirunelveli\n|M\n|Government Tirunelveli Medical College Hospital\n| rowspan=\"3\" |attended Delhi religious conference\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;background: #D3D3D3;\"|102\n!1\n| style=\"text-align:center;background:#ffff96;\"|'''T/PTP'''\n|\n|Thoothukudi\n|M\n|Government Thoothukudi Medical College Hospital\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;background: #D3D3D3;\"|103-120\n!18\n| style=\"text-align:center;background:#ffff96;\"|'''T/PTP'''\n|\n|Namakkal district (Paramathi Velur, Rasipuram)\n|M\n|Namakkal Medical College Hospital and Rasipuram GH\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;background: #D3D3D3;\"|121-124\n!4\n| style=\"text-align:center;background:#ffff96;\"|'''T/PTP'''\n|\n|Chennai\n|M\n|Rajiv Gandhi Government General Hospital and private hospitals\n|\n|}\n\n\n=== Charts ===\n{{Graph:Chart\n | height=300\n | width = 