 commits to pay 160,000 contract labourers despite disruption in work|date=30 March 2020|work=The Economic Times|access-date=31 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Central Armed Police Forces]]\n|{{INRConvert|116|c|lk=on|year=2020}}<ref name=\":6\" />\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Adani Foundation]]\n|{{INRConvert|100|c|lk=on|year=2020}}<ref name=\":4\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.business-standard.com/multimedia/video-gallery/general/covid-19-patanjali-to-contribute-rs-25-crore-to-pm-cares-fund-101941.htm|title=Donations Pour In For PM Cares Fund For Coronavirus: From Akshay Kumar To Champion Shooter Esha Singh|last=day|first=Jinal Bhatt 1|date=2020-03-30|website=Mashable India|language=en-in|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-03-31}}</ref>\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Bajaj Group]]\n|{{INRConvert|100|c|lk=on|year=2020}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fortuneindia.com/macro/tata-group-commits-1500-crore-to-fight-covid-19/104341|title=Tata group commits \u20b91,500 crore to fight Covid-19|website=www.fortuneindia.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-01}}</ref>\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[JSW Group]]\n|{{INRConvert|100|c|lk=on|year=2020}}<ref>{{Cite news|last=Dilipkumar|first=Bhavya|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/company/corporate-trends/jsw-announces-rs-100-crores-contribution-to-pm-cares-converts-some-facilities-into-isolation-wards/articleshow/74872384.cms|title=JSW announces Rs 100 crores contribution to PM-CARES, converts some facilities into isolation wards|date=29 March 2020|work=The Economic Ttimes|access-date=31 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Torrent Group]]\n|{{INRConvert|100|c|lk=on|year=2020}}<ref>{{Cite news|last=Jayakumar|first=PB|url=https://www.businesstoday.in/current/corporate/torrent-group-commits-rs-100-crore-to-fight-coronavirus-pandemic/story/399668.html|title=Torrent Group commits Rs 100 crore to fight coronavirus pandemic|date=31 March 2020|work=Business Today|access-date=31 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|\n|\n|-\